Issue: Java Heap Space Exception running the JUnit-Test src.test.java.de.tudarmstadt.ukp.manuelwick.dkpro.experiments.terrier_indexing()

To reconstruct the error do following:
 - Checkout the project from SVN
 - Reference needed libraries (in fact use all libs in directories dkpro, miscellaneous, tika)
 - Go into source folder src/test/java class de.tudarmstadt.ukp.manuelwick.dkpro.experiments
 - Change "rootDir" to the folder that contains "documents" where the CRM-Data is in
 ( e.g. /home/manuel/myfiles/testfolder, that contains CRM in /home/manuel/myfiles/testfolder/documents/[99-109])
 - Run terrier_indexing()
 - Go get some coffee